1999-11-29  Masanao Izumo <mo@goice.co.jp>

    * Version 2.8.1 released.

1999-11-29  Masanao Izumo <mo@goice.co.jp>

    * timidity/timidity.c,interface/{gtk_c.c,motif_c.c,w32g_i.c,w32g_util.c,
