    * timidity/{timidity.c,playmidi.c,playmidi.h} (new_chorus_voice_alternate):
      To use the surround sound instead of detuned chorus.
      It is enabled with -EFchorus=2 or -EFchorus=2,level option
      (level := [0..63])

