1999-04-17  Masanao Izumo <mo@goice.co.jp>

    * Version 2.0.0 released.

1999-04-17  Masanao Izumo <mo@goice.co.jp>

    * timidity/playmidi.c: Fix portamento controls.

1999-04-16  Masanao Izumo <mo@goice.co.jp>

